    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/f38932f847fc7020b769d5476fa43757.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Feelings is a third-person adventure and puzzle game where players follow Sarah's inner journey, accompanied by her faithful mentor and friend, Toothbun. Together, they embark on an incredible journey of self-discovery as they explore floating islands that represent the character's memories and feelings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/6bb31a42588d379d9b9bf10914aabaf2.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/6f33dd7596cf61b9136ccc5c93751555.poster.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/6f33dd7596cf61b9136ccc5c93751555.webm?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/6f33dd7596cf61b9136ccc5c93751555.mp4?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features different biomes, animals, nostalgic elements, an immersive soundtrack and charismatic characters. Each stage is an emotional journey inside Sarah's mind, molding itself to the demands of the story, and delving into the memories of the character as she progresses on her journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/df09a754b67604b2cbd2e17fc629ac27.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/eee49301561c947f269efd74af50ecd5.poster.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/eee49301561c947f269efd74af50ecd5.webm?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/eee49301561c947f269efd74af50ecd5.mp4?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sarah finds herself in an introspective process, taking on the form of a child and facing arduous challenges for her emotions, symbolized by the islands scattered around the game map.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/d454ba2be13ea33e6e4e974f4e9db48f.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/4cba904fc695644d31e131924e82c515.poster.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/4cba904fc695644d31e131924e82c515.webm?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/4cba904fc695644d31e131924e82c515.mp4?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sarah carries with her a special camera, an amulet capable of capturing the hidden layers of 'Feelings'. Through it, explore a universe full of mysteries and hidden secrets. Discover camouflaged objects, uncover stories buried by time and forge your own narrative as you immerse yourself in the character's feelings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/026e40c7ca018cee16b6f4191092650f.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/7cd2dadc9b59b6691c39b3ec5c695e02.poster.avif?t=1731683382\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/7cd2dadc9b59b6691c39b3ec5c695e02.webm?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793580/extras/7cd2dadc9b59b6691c39b3ec5c695e02.mp4?t=1731683382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;Toothbun&quot;, Sarah's loyal companion, will be present throughout this journey, supporting the girl on her way. As well as helping to solve puzzles, he is adorably endearing.",
